oke out in the Gaza Strip between Israel and Hamas. Since October 8, Lebanese and Palestinian factions in Lebanon, led by Hezbollah, have been exchanging daily shelling with the Israeli army across the Blue Line, resulting in the deaths of hundreds, mostly on the Lebanese side.
